description:
In this video I'm looking back at the first videos I've ever uploaded to YouTube from the 2013-2015 range. I'll talk about the process of making these videos, why they even got made and other stuff I just want to add to the video.

Note. This video currently has no English subtitles available and is intended for audiences who can understand Estonian. Subtitles may come later, however since this is a very long video, it might take a while for me to make them.
